<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <% include ../partials/head %>
</head>

<script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
        $("#modal-open").click();

        var write = function(contents) {
            var postdata = {
                'user_name': $("#user_name").val(),
                'user_position': $("#user_position").val(),
                'user_interest': $("#user_interest").val(),
                'user_email': $("#user_email").val(),
                'user_description': $("#user_description").val()
            };

            $.post('/invest', postdata, function() {
            });
        };

        $.get('/load', function(data) {
            $("#user_submit").click(function(evt) {
                write();
                alert("입력 완료! " + $("#user_name").val() + " 님 감사합니다");
                window.location.replace("/board");
            });
        });
    });
</script>

<body id="mainpage-body">
    <header>
        <div class="header-content">
            <div id='main' class="header-content-inner title">
                <img id="title_image" src="images/VIRUS_logo_white.png" alt="" />
                <p id="title_words">LIVE NETWORKING PROGRAM</p>
                <hr style="margin: 0" />
                <table id="table-main">
                    <tr class="tr_border">
                        <th>이름(Name)</th>
                        <td><input id='user_name' type='text' placeholder='Hyunseok Moon' /></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="tr_border">
                        <th>신분(Position)</th>
                        <td><input id='user_position' type='text' placeholder='Startup / Freelancer / VC / General / Student' /></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="tr_border">
                        <th>관심 분야(Interest)</th>
                        <td><input id='user_interest' type='text' placeholder='Machine Learning' /></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="tr_border">
                        <th>이메일(E-mail)</th>
                        <td><input id='user_email' type='text' placeholder='hyunseok.moon@vi-rus.network' /></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>한 줄 소개(Description)</th>
                        <td><input id='user_description' type='text' placeholder='Core director of VIRUS-NETWORK' /></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr style="height: 15px">
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="2">
                            <input id='user_submit' type='button' value='제출(Submit)' />
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Button trigger modal -->
    <button id="modal-open" type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal" style="visibility: hidden">
    </button>

    <!-- Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="myModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
                    <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">네트워킹 보드 | Networking Board</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>한 줄 소개 프로그램에 참여해 주셔서 감사합니다.</p>
                    <p>한 줄 소개 프로그램은 참가자 분들의 네트워킹을 더욱 원활하게 형성할 수 있도록 제작된 프로그램입니다. 작성하신 양식은 핸드폰을 비롯한 메인 무대 화면에도 확인가능합니다. 관심이 있는 VC 혹은 Startup 기업을 찾으시면, 기재된 이메일을 통해 네트워킹 맺으실 수 있습니다. 모든 사항은 영어로 작성 부탁드립니다.</p>
                    <hr/>
                    <p>Thank you for participating “Describing your company in a sentence.”</p>
                    <p>This program is made for your better environments of networking. The form which you wrote will be able to check on your phone and the screen on the main stage. If you find interesting VC or Startups, you can make networking with them via E-mail which will be shown. Referred following example, fill the blank on the below. Every blank should be written in English.</p>
                    <hr/>
                    <p>네트워킹 보드 확인(Check networking board) : <a href="/board">ORDERED</a> | <a href="/board-random">RANDOM</a></p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <p>본 프로그램은 청년 창업 문화 확산을 위해 힘쓰는 <a href="http://virus.network"><strong>VIRUS</strong></a> 에서 제작하였습니다.</p>
                    <p>This program has been brought to you by the <a href="http://virus.network"><strong>Value Influencer to Rocket/Uprise Startup - VIRUS</strong></a></p>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">확인</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <% include ../partials/body_script %>
</body>

</html>
